{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_BeShadowyFoe}}
'''A_BeShadowyFoe'''<br />
(no parameters)

Sets the calling actor's render style to Translucent, gives it the SHADOW flag, and clears its FRIENDLY flag.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Acolyte}} and derived classes.

